    "title": "Senior Revenue Manager at The Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Grow your career with The Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Revenue Manager for our Vijayawada team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout The Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited:\nThe Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Revenue Management\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with The Lalit Hotels Advisory Limited!",
